  <script data-testid="inline-script">
   function consentCookieState() {
    const PENDING = false;
    const NECESSARY = false;
    const UNNECESSARY = true;
    let cookieValue;
    let parsedCookieValue;


    function getCookieValue(str) {
        var cookieData = document.cookie.match("(^|[^;]+)\s*" + str + "\s*=\s*([^;]+)");
        return (cookieData ? cookieData.pop() : "");
    }

    function extractConsent(obj) {
        return obj.consentGiven;
    }

    function evalConsent(val) {
        return (typeof val === "boolean" && val === true);
    }

    function getConsentState(consentsCategories) {
        var hasAcceptedAll = consentsCategories.map(extractConsent).every(evalConsent);
        return hasAcceptedAll ? UNNECESSARY : NECESSARY;
    }

    try {
        cookieValue = getCookieValue("cookie_consents");
        parsedCookieValue = JSON.parse(cookieValue);

        if (parsedCookieValue.content.consents.length >= 1) {
            return getConsentState(parsedCookieValue.content.consents[0].categories);
        }
        return PENDING;
    } catch (e) {
        return PENDING;
    }
}
